title: How I actually make myself DO my routine.
itunes:title: How I actually make myself DO my routine.
description:
I have my routines. But I also know HOW to make myself do them. In this podcast, not only will I tell you how I've figured out what routines work for me, I tell you how I've decided I can show up for myself and do those things that I know make me feel good in the end.
